ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
PrecisAppointment of KAREN McMILLAN of Toronto, Ontario, to be a full-time member of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Toronto Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of eight months or a period expiring on the day prior to the coming into force of the Balance Refugee Reform Act, whichever periods ends earlier, effective March 19, 2012.
